sc_cat_item.description:
Product Specs
  • Material: 100% Polyester Stretch Textured Serge Weave, 7.0 oz.
  • Nano Moisture Wicking technology pulls moisture away from your body, keeping you dry and comfortable
  • 4 Pockets, including:
    • Quarter-top front pockets
    • 2 back pockets
  • Closure: bar-tacked double crush-proof hook and eye
  • 5 Belt Loops: ⅞" wide of double thickness with stitching on the face side ⅜" from each edge
  • Waistband: Covert flex waistband provides 3" stretch for added comfort while holding up a duty belt
  • Triple-stitched crotch prevents seam failure
  • Front and back permanent creases provide a professional appearance
Sizing Information
  • Fit: Men’s “Essential Fit” pattern features tapered legs for a professional and comfortable fit
  • Please refer to our detailed size chart for additional information
Care Instructions
  • Washing Instructions: Machine washable
  • Drying Instructions: Tumble dry low
  • Ironing Instructions: Use warm iron if needed
sc_cat_item.name: Uniform Pants
